LanguageData.LetterPanDaPasses: A pair of pandas came to the area. This extremely rare beast is gentle in nature, but can become extremely dangerous when angered. At the same time, its leather is also very precious.\n\n This kind of panda is very strict with the environment, so if you want to tame them, you need to hurry up.
LanguageData.LetterTuJiPasses: A group of lost native chickens wander here. If you want to catch some, raise or kill them, you should hurry up, because they will soon run to other places.
